caller_intent: Frank Grubs wanted to clarify his insurance renewal details and make a partial payment toward his upcoming premium.
resolution_steps: Amanda confirmed Frank's account details, showing his last payment was $1,629.60 on October 23 and the next renewal amount of $404.72 due January 31.
Frank requested to pay $200 toward the renewal, which Amanda processed via credit card.
Amanda sent a confirmation email and informed Frank he would receive a renewal notice in the mail by January.
knowledge_required: Insurance renewal processes and payment schedules
summary: Frank Grubs contacted Alliance Insurance to address confusion about his insurance payments and make a partial renewal payment. Amanda clarified his account details, processed a $200 credit card payment toward his $404.72 January 31 renewal, and confirmed he would receive a renewal notice in the mail.
